58:12.864 --> 58:16.033
You know that you're the most
rebellious one in here.

58:17.160 --> 58:19.995
It's pretty impressive.

58:19.996 --> 58:22.789
Maybe if you spent
a little less time fighting,

58:22.790 --> 58:24.374
you wouldn't be so tired.

58:24.375 --> 58:26.418
Yeah, but what
am I supposed to do, just...

58:26.419 --> 58:28.086
Don't interrupt me.

58:28.087 --> 58:30.380
I'm sorry, sir.

58:30.381 --> 58:31.757
Come on.
Look at you.

58:31.758 --> 58:34.635
