all right?

58:46.439 --> 58:49.525
W-would you do that?

58:50.693 --> 58:52.986
Phil, I think
we're done here.

58:52.987 --> 58:55.155
Take him away.

58:56.866 --> 58:58.116
Wait!
Wait!

58:58.117 --> 58:59.618
Wait, wait, wait, wait!
No, no, no, no!

58:59.619 --> 59:00.869
