59:06.334 --> 59:07.834
Hey, you're not really
gonna tell them

59:07.835 --> 59:08.835
to take it easy on him,
are you?

59:08.836 --> 59:10.087
Oh, my God.
Of course not.

59:10.088 --> 59:11.547
Are you kidding me?
He was faking it, anyway.

59:11.548 --> 59:12.631
I can tell.

59:12.632 --> 59:15.133
There's no way he's getting out
of here right now.

59:15.134 --> 59:18.428
During meals and whenever
they are in the prison yard.

59:18.429 --> 59:21.098
Oh, hello, 8612.

59:21.099 --> 59:23.350
Welcome back.

59:23.351 --> 59:26.144
Get your ass
back in line, boy.

59:26.145 --> 59:28.438
As I was saying,

59:28.439 --> 59:31.608
prisoners must remain silent
during rest periods,

59:31.609 --> 59:35.946
after lights out, during meals,
and outside the prison yard.

59:35.947 --> 59:37.656
- Rule number two...
- What happened?

59:37.657 --> 59:39.366
Prisoners must eat
at meal times...

59:39.367 --> 59:42.077
I couldn't get out.

59:42.078 --> 59:43.745
What do you mean, you couldn't
get out of the contract?

59:43.746 --> 59:44.871
Hey!

59:44.872 --> 59:46.873
No talking on the line,
you two.

59:46.874 --> 59:49.042
- Contract don't mean shit.
- Rule number three.

59:49.043 --> 59:52.629
I mean I couldn't get out.
I mean they wouldn't let me out.

59:52.630 --> 59:54.047
This is all real.

59:54.048 --> 59:55.382
This is all real.

59:55.383 --> 59:56.633
This is all real.
This is all real.

59:56.634 --> 59:57.968
