01:00:49.812 --> 01:00:51.688
Uh...

01:00:51.689 --> 01:00:54.608
We‒we hit a breaking point
last night,

01:00:54.609 --> 01:00:59.237
and, um,
8612 is gone.

01:00:59.238 --> 01:01:01.031
