01:01:19.842 --> 01:01:21.593
and you have tampered
with the integrity

01:01:21.594 --> 01:01:22.928
of the entire enterprise.

01:01:22.929 --> 01:01:24.846
Phil, we were following
protocol.

01:01:24.847 --> 01:01:26.640
The kid was
in a serious crisis.

01:01:26.641 --> 01:01:27.683
