01:02:45.303 --> 01:02:47.888
I'm sorry.

01:02:47.889 --> 01:02:48.930
I don't buy any of this.

01:02:48.931 --> 01:02:51.933
No, I don't imagine
you would.

01:02:53.436 --> 01:02:55.312
This is bullshit.

01:02:55.313 --> 01:02:57.898
