concerned about our son.

01:09:14.233 --> 01:09:15.274
Okay.

01:09:15.276 --> 01:09:17.193
Well, what...
what...

01:09:17.194 --> 01:09:18.944
what seems to be
the problem?

01:09:18.946 --> 01:09:21.238
